OL,3,CWarning as social media scammers
OL,4,Cimpersonate 'major' UK airlines
OL,6,FSocial media scammers are
OL,7,Fimpersonating every major airline
OL,8,Foperating in the UK, according to new
OL,9,Fanalysis.
OL,11,FConsumer group Which? said fraudsters
OL,12,Fon X ` formerly known as Twitter ` are
OL,13,Fresponding to messages sent to
OL,14,Fofficial accounts.
OL,16,FIt found scammers impersonating to ask
OL,17,Ffor enough information to allow them
OL,18,Fto commit identity fraud.
