OL,3,CWarning as social media scammers
OL,4,Cimpersonate 'major' UK airlines
OL,6,FWhich? said one of its researchers who
OL,7,Fposted a message to the official
OL,8,Faccount for Wizz Air to ask if a
OL,9,Fflight was delayed received responses
OL,10,Ffrom two fake accounts "almost
OL,11,Fimmediately".
OL,13,FIt added: "Both used near-identical
OL,14,Flanguage, apologising for the
OL,15,Finconvenience, stating that they had
OL,16,F'already escalated this matter to the
OL,17,Frelevant department' and requesting a
OL,18,F'reachable WhatsApp number for
OL,19,Fassistance' via DM (direct message).
