OL,3,CWarning as social media scammers
OL,4,Cimpersonate 'major' UK airlines
OL,6,F"We found examples of bogus X accounts
OL,7,Fimpersonating every major airline
OL,8,Foperating in the UK, including British
OL,9,FAirways, easyJet, Jet2, Ryanair, Tui,
OL,10,FVirgin Atlantic and Wizz Air.
OL,12,F"We also discovered that fake accounts
OL,13,Fare often quicker to respond than the
OL,14,Fgenuine airlines, but they also
OL,15,Finterrupt existing conversations
OL,16,Fbetween you and airlines, which can be
OL,17,Fharder to spot."
OL,19,FX has been approached for a comment.
