OL,4,Cimpersonate 'major' UK airlines
OL,6,FWhich? said reporting fake accounts to
OL,7,FX "seems to have limited success",
OL,8,Fwith most of the posts and accounts it
OL,9,Fflagged remaining live.
OL,11,FIt advised passengers to verify if an
OL,12,Faccount is genuine by checking for a
OL,13,Flink on an official website, when it
OL,14,Fjoined X and how many followers it has.
