OL,3,CWarning as social media scammers
OL,4,Cimpersonate 'major' UK airlines
OL,6,FRocio Concha, Which? director of
OL,7,Fpolicy and advocacy, said fraudsters
OL,8,Fare "shamelessly trying to trick
OL,9,Fairline customers seeking urgent
OL,10,Fcustomer service advice". She
OL,11,Fdescribed the situation as part of an
OL,12,F"epidemic of fraud".
OL,14,F"X and other social media platforms
OL,15,Fneed to be held to a high standard and
OL,16,FOfcom must not shy away from taking
OL,17,Fstrong enforcement action, including
OL,18,Ffines, against firms if they break the
OL,19,Flaw," she added.
